gw.plugin.policylocation

Interface LocationRiskAssessmentPlugin

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.guidewire.pl.system.integration.plugins.internal.InternalPlugin, java.rmi.Remote

    public interface LocationRiskAssessmentPlugin
extends com.guidewire.pl.system.integration.plugins.internal.InternalPlugin
    This plugin will generate the request to the risk assessment service provider and retrieves assessment results.

    • Method Detail

      • getRiskAssessmentResultsForPeriod

        java.util.List<InboundLocationRiskAssessmentTempStore> getRiskAssessmentResultsForPeriod(OutboundPeriodRiskAssessmentTempStore requestDataList,
                                                                                         LocationRiskAssessmentParameters params,
                                                                                         RiskAssessmentErrorCollector errorCollector)
        Sends the request to the risk assessment service provider and retrieves assessment result for all the locations
        Parameters:
        requestDataList - list of Policy Locations
        params - parameters to pass into the Risk Assessment Service
        Returns:
        A map of location risk assessment results by location from a risk assessment service provider

      • navigateToRiskAssessmentSystem

        void navigateToRiskAssessmentSystem(java.util.List<java.lang.String> parameters)
        Navigates to the Spotlight interactive service with the following format: https://spotlightUrl/#/v1/urlPrefix/{param1}/paramsUrlFragment/{param2}/returnUrlFragment/{param3} It will take three parameters as described below.
        Parameters:
        parameters - - List of parameters used to navigate to risk assessment system param1 - The Policy Center Url i.e. http://pcUrl/service/Spotlight/ param2 - The pc param servlet i.e. LocationDetail.do?LocationID=######### param3 - The return pc return servlet i.e. SpotlightReturn.do

      • getRiskAssessmentDataHash

        DataHasher getRiskAssessmentDataHash(OutboundLocationRiskAssessmentTempStore outboundRiskAssessmentData)
        Returns a hash of the 'important' policy location fields, to determine 'staleness'.
        Returns:
        a DataHasher that can accept the provided OutboundLocationRiskAssessmentTempStore entity for hashing.
